author: KEXP
description: Multi-instrumentalist Daniel Kadawatha captivates audiences with hypnotic grooves under the musical outfit @arcdesoleil. With guitar-driven psych rock off his latest release 'Lumin Rain', Kadawatha demonstrates raw power Live on KEXP, sharing a performance of "Midnight In Saqqara" and more from the album.
title: Arc De Soleil performs "Lumin Rain" and more Live on KEXP
